{"TopicId":202067,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Aeris 4A Challenge","CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-28T22:49:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-28T22:49:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Aeris 4A is a reasonably capable \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E spaceplane, able to do a Mun or Minmus flyby, or even go interplanetary with proper gravity assists. It can also dock with other Aeris 4A. How far can you take one?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou could try to fly a single Aeris 4A but might not make it too far. However, using one as a fuel tanker is an option...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Death Engineering","CreatedById":68528,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-27T18:01:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223962743\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022202067\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619650185\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207172\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022camacju\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/28/2021 at 6:49 PM, camacju said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, using one as a fuel tanker is an option...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOnly one?\u00A0 I just refueled one in orbit with 3 Aeris\u0027 .. Aerae? \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u00A0\u003Cem\u003EAnd \u003C/em\u003Elanded them all at the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E!\u00A0 I want to recreate that loading-screen shot of the Aeris around Laythe.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-05-27T18:52:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually forgot that I posted this thread! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI recently did exactly that, and took an Aeris to Laythe and back. But I haven\u0027t found the motivation to edit the video yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}